    "The number of block structures used in the study can be increased much more if desired.",
    "However, this will significantly increase the complexity of the model and the training time.",
    "For this reason, the number of blocks is left at the optimum level in the cell-SegUNet model.",
    "The output layer used in the study is a new structure that was developed specifically for the model and is not used in UNet-based approaches in the literature.The basic logic of this structure is based on the fact that when more than one feature is used, one feature may increase performance while another feature may decrease performance.",
    "This situation is undesirable and an attempt was made to prevent this with the output layer used in the study."
